 {"id":"bd-15r9","title":"Implement end-to-end test scripts with comprehensive logging","description":"# Implement End-to-End Test Scripts

## Task Overview

Create comprehensive e2e test scripts that verify the entire rich output system works
correctly as an integrated whole, with detailed logging for debugging.

## Why E2E Tests?

Unit tests verify individual components work, but we need e2e tests to verify:
- Components integrate correctly
- Output mode detection flows through entire system
- Global instance works correctly across modules
- Real terminal output is correct
- Agent detection affects all output correctly

## Test Scripts

### tests/e2e/test_full_startup.rs

```rust
//\! E2E test: Full server startup banner flow

use fastapi_output::prelude::*;
